					<description><![CDATA[<p>With over 15 years in packaging machinery, we explain the pros &#38; cons of gear pump fillers, why we’ve been cautious, and what to look for in 2025. Make an informed choice. Gear Pump Filling Machines: An Honest Review from a 15-Year Packaging Veteran If you’ve been evaluating filling equipment lately, you’ve undoubtedly been pitched [&#8230;]</p>
