<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The chemical industry uses many dangerous chemicals and corrosive liquids, and the danger of human operation is relatively high. Automated machines are also better at protecting personnel’s safety. Higher precision also prevents leaks and allows products to be handled correctly.</p>



