					<description><![CDATA[<p>Lotion knowledge The primary target audience of the lotion market is women, who are driving explosive growth in purchasing power year after year, according to global market data. Many see the enormous profit potential in the lotion industry, which has inspired countless individuals worldwide to dive into lotion production. As a result, numerous brands with [&#8230;]</p>
