<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a class="" href="https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Npack-Automatic-Servo-Pump-Filling-Skincare_1601233481158.html?spm=a2700.galleryofferlist.normal_offer.d_title.439413a0lbhK9G" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img alt="What You Need to Know About Lotion Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer" title="What You Need to Know About Lotion Filling Machine-China Liquid Filling Machine Leading Manufacturer" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="720" height="720" src="https://www.npackpm.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/2025101704133356.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-3740" title="Lotion Filling Machine"/></a></figure>



